snippet.title: Britney Spears Speaks On Justin Timberlake Trying To Be Her Friend
snippet.description:
Britney Spears Speaks On Justin Timberlake Trying To Be Her Friend

Britney Spears is finally free from her conservatorship and here come all the people who stayed silent for over a decade crawling back and trying to be her friend.
But is Justin Timberlake one of these people? Or does he genuinely care about Britney?
Well, Britney’s fans have A LOT to say about this since we all know how Justin treated Britney after they broke up.
But what about Britney? Is she ready to forgive Justin?
